
.. app.py server
.. ^^^^^^^^^^^^^

.. ^ Title not specified here so I can put a custom paragraph in between.

Sub-commands
~~~~~~~~~~~~

- ``start``: Start HTTP server.
- ``stop``: Stop HTTP server.
- ``restart``: Restart HTTP server.

Options
~~~~~~~

.. The defaults are stated in the docopt docstring. Not specified here to keep this docstring
.. as generic as possible.

- ``--host=<host>`` Host name.
- ``--port=<port>`` Port number.
